==The greatest heroes of the land==
===Talking to Achietties or trying to enter the guild===
* '''Achietties:''' Greetings. Welcome to the Heroes' Guild.
* '''Achietties:''' Only the greatest heroes of this land may gain entrance to this guild.
* {{tcond|If the player's skill levels are lower than the quest requirements.}}
** {{tbox|Before starting this quest, be aware that one or more of your skill levels are lower than what is required to fully complete it.}}
* {{tselect|Start the Heroes' Quest?}}
* {{topt|Yes.}}
** '''Player:''' I'm a hero. May I apply to join?
** {{tcond|If the player doesn't have the quest requirements to start the quest:}}
