** {{tselect|Select an option}}
** {{topt|Any hints on getting the armband?}}
*** '''Player:''' Any hints on getting the thieves armband?
*** '''Achietties:''' I'm sure you have the relevant contacts to find out about that.
*** {{tact|end}}
